Investigation: 设计了一种人Arg opal sup-tRNA，并将其表达在含有XPA基因无义突变（R207X）的XP12ROSV细胞中。结果表明，这种抑制性tRNA能够部分恢复细胞对紫外线照射的耐受性，并提高了DNA修复效率。
Citation: Panchal, R. G., Wang, S., McDermott, J. & Link, C. J. Jr. Partial functional correction of xeroderma pigmentosum group A cells by suppressor tRNA. Hum. Gene Ther. 10, 2209–2219 (1999).

Safety: high safety (caused no discernible readthrough at endogenous native stop codons, as determined by ribosome profiling)
Investigation: 用工程化 tRNA 抑制无义突变：在小鼠静脉和气管内LNP输注IVT sup-tRNASer；在R1162X-CFTR患者囊性纤维化细胞模型和上皮细胞中转染sup-tRNASer和sup-tRNAArg
Citation: Albers, S. et al. Engineered tRNAs suppress nonsense mutations in cells and in vivo. Nature 618, 842–848 (2023).
